354
00:27:34,599 --> 00:27:35,239
Yuehua.

355
00:27:36,439 --> 00:27:38,280
Dunia sangat keras pada wanita.

356
00:27:40,359 --> 00:27:41,790
Sekali kau mengambil jalan pintas,…

357
00:27:42,359 --> 00:27:44,680
